          <title>Mexico tests cellphone app allowing migrants to send alert if they are about to be detained in US</title>
          <description><![CDATA[MEXICO CITY (AP) — Mexico is developing a cellphone app that will allow migrants to warn relatives and local consulates if they think they are about to be detained by the U.S. immigration department, a senior official said Friday.]]></description>
          <guid>https://majordigest.com/tech/2024/12/27/mexico-tests-cellphone-app-allowing-migrants-to-send-alert-if-they-are-about-to-be-detained-in-us/</guid>
