          <title>Cyberattack hits Japan Airlines, delaying flights for holiday travelers</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Japan Airlines said it was hit by a cyberattack Thursday, causing delays to more than 20 domestic flights but the carrier said it was able to stop the onslaught and restore its systems hours later. There was no impact on flight safety, it said.]]></description>
